    (:problem "An animation loops through a full revolution — τ radians." :program "(define (revolution-fraction t) (/ t math/tau))
(revolution-fraction (/ math/tau 4))" :explanation "Divide by τ to get fraction of a revolution." :meta "math/tau is the correct verb because it names 2π directly. Using (* 2 math/pi) works but hides the intent of 'full revolution'.")
